        Lines ~72-130. The 11-tile palette to replace. Shows drag-drop wiring with React Flow.
      </pattern>
      <pattern name="Fluent v9 semantic tokens" location=".claude/skills/fluent-v9-component/SKILL.md">
        How to use `tokens.colorNeutralBackground1` etc., FluentProvider patterns, dark-mode adaptation.
